&lt;p&gt;We welcome applications from enthusiastic and experienced Clinical Psychologists to join our well established Adult Step 4 Psychology team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will provide psychological input to Adult clients in West Cheshire who are referred through the Primary Care Mental Health Stepped care model.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be able to draw upon a range of therapeutic models and be able to work in a time limited way in primary care offering individual and group interventions to clients.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We would consider applications from more newly qualified psychologists and appoint on a preceptorship basis as appropriate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information about the service and the position please contact either Karen Flockhart or Suzanne Riddell&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Karen Flockhart Consultant Clinical Psychologist Email address karen.flockhart@nhs.net Telephone number 01244397575 &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Suzanne Riddell Clinical Psychologist Telephone number 01244 397575&lt;/p&gt;
